  <brief_title>Study Comparing Two Strategies of Exercise in Breast and Colon Cancer Survivors and Their Impact on Fatigue</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Study Comparing Two Strategies of Physical Activity in Long-term Breast and Colon Cancer Survivors and Their Impact on Fatigue</official_title>
